subject: Playoff Games
Golf
lead_paragraph: Ray Stewart shot a four-under 68 yesterday to take a four-shot lead after two rounds of the Champions Tour Boeing Classic in Snoqualmie, Wash. Stewart, who survived a 10-man playoff in a qualifier for this tournament, was at 10-under 134.
